n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想一生霸住你！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"25a96314765dfdfdf7bda04dfd8b977bd7d19133","tid":469010,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:17:58.000Z","msg":"其實佢地有咩值得人鐘意 又抄g dragon<br />\n妹妹仔既錢都呃 話咩可以幫手買演唱會飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歌又唔係佢地作 唱又唔好聽<br />\n鐘意佢係其實係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e96fa4ba08770c6867f5277c8e7e7c7d64c637","tid":469010,"uid":56716,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:24:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢地有咩值得人鐘意 又抄g dragon<br />\n妹妹仔既錢都呃 話咩可以幫手買演唱會飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歌又唔係佢地作 唱又唔好聽<br />\n鐘意佢係其實係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n歌真係tommy作架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔鍾意佢嘅咪剩係不斷放大佢地嘅負面野，真心鍾意佢地嘅係會欣賞佢地好嘅一面。無錯tommy以前係衰過，但佢而家都好努力工作同埋佢一直都無放棄作歌，佢最霉嗰段時間都有keep住佢曲，垃圾一曲就係佢作嚟鼓勵自己。E-kids出道到而家，好多歌都係tommy負責作曲的，最新嗰兩首都係。不過就算我點講都好，唔鍾意佢地嘅都唔會改變諗法架啦，只會不停重提負面野同會考幾分。"},{"pid":"7f259c38c2d610a564604a4b61c5510ecf2c5583","tid":469010,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:26:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>童年回憶<br />\n<br />\n一定支持</blockquote><br />\n巴打會去嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕要食黃牛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17fc6dbf223626860c3403e18b244f5f11e7770","tid":469010,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:27:10.000Z","msg":"就算知道啲歌係tommy作咁又點？盲反嘅人只會不斷重複恥笑佢地，笑佢地咁都有人鍾意，仲屈埋我係打手添（條友仲未入嚟）"},{"pid":"67fc29267823b892b6be06c02e3b114c85348ed3","tid":469010,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:28:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>童年回憶<br />\n<br />\n一定支持</blockquote><br />\n巴打會去嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕要食黃牛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">諗住優先訂飛當日射波捕住部電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"6261b27fc1ec257f0ce2755ec714c07374c48c16","tid":469010,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:33:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cac2d29764acc9446ba55d0a79801a2cd8fb54eb","tid":469010,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:40:16.000Z","msg":"We are E-kids!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d94e8d69cbb22793d997fc6daa55ac9e4a23962","tid":469010,"uid":56716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:49:15.000Z","msg":"MK-POP始祖E-kids又開騷啦！明年2月9及10日再踩主場旺角，喺麥花臣場館舉行「E-kids AGAIN?Conect 2018」，阮民安（Tommy）接受《蘋果》電話訪問表示：「好開心，呢個演唱會所有嘢源自上年個唱延續，上年真係好慶幸，我哋重組可以開賣飛演唱會，仲要極速爆咗，當時投資者話加場，但我哋三個唔想加場，希望每一年E-kids都可以開到演唱會。」<br />\n<br />\n結果，E-kids明年真係再開騷，Tommy仔話：「有投資單位同我哋傾，覺得我哋好努力，堅持咗咁多年，仲可以死唔去開到騷，好開心有投資者慧眼識英雄，今次我哋再要求喺麥花臣，MK-POP梗係要喺旺角紥根。2018年做第二次騷，仲有新歌，又飛日本拍MV，全部都係錢，大家都知喺香港做音樂搵唔到錢，尤其我哋呢啲又唔係咁出名嘅藝人更加辛苦，今次演唱會希望進步一格，去年開一場，今年開兩場，其實壓力好大，對我哋係考驗，要對得住觀眾，真金白銀買飛睇E-kids。」"},{"pid":"a79107c8d5bf60d81dcbfd4bf3ce31a0a675ffa5","tid":469010,"uid":50712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:15:01.000Z","msg":"麥花臣真係公廁黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402cfc9f685cdb0daa8ae95a392922b9428bfeb7","tid":469010,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/140559_14f4234e004cf86bf1f3ba1377b4aa14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F140559_14f4234e004cf86bf1f3ba1377b4aa14.jpg&h=80296995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nE-kids &amp; W-inds<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}